item.title: aw man, tomorrow's a holiday!!!
item.description: ##23:16 Thursday 22 November 2012 I was all ready to code code code tomorrow; I left my machine on, paper strewn across my desk; I didn’t even push my latest changes to Github! I might do a dry run tomorrow in some random directory on my site… if I do, I can post it here; yay! If I don’t, know I’m enjoying a holiday; yay!
